---
// Override of Starlight's `PageTitle`.
//
// The repo `docs/` Markdown is the single source of truth and is also rendered
// on GitHub, so every page opens with an `# H1` heading in its body. Starlight
// additionally renders the frontmatter `title` as its own page `<h1>`, which
// produced a second, identical heading on every page.
//
// We render nothing visible here — the body `# H1` is the page title — but keep
// the `#_top` anchor that Starlight's "Skip to content" link and the mobile
// "Overview" table-of-contents entry scroll to.
---

<div id="_top"></div>
